<Base
  title="Affiliate Disclosure"
  description="How SoloStack makes money and how we keep reviews honest."
>
  <h1>Affiliate disclosure</h1>
  <p>
    Some links on SoloStack are affiliate links. If you click one and buy
    or sign up, the company may pay us a commission. It never costs you anything
    extra, and it never changes what we recommend: every tool is tested hands-on
    and reviewed the same way whether or not it has an affiliate program.
  </p>
  <p>
    Posts containing affiliate links carry a disclosure notice at the top of the
    article, before any such link, in line with FTC Endorsement Guides.
  </p>
</Base>
